Spec: Update Checker Service
Purpose:
  Check the local SpecDD bootstrap version against the latest available release.

Structure:
  update-checker.ts: Update checker service implementation.
  update-checker.test.ts: Update checker tests.

Owns:
  update-checker.ts
  update-checker.test.ts

References:
  ../bootstrap-metadata/service.sdd
  ../logger/service.sdd
  ../specdd-version/service.sdd
  ../distribution-client/service.sdd

Must:
  Accept Logger, DistributionClient, SpecDDVersion, and BootstrapMetadata through constructor parameters.
  Expose check(request) for the check-update command flow.
  Accept the current working directory as the target directory.
  Read local .specdd/bootstrap.md front matter Version through BootstrapMetadata when the file exists.
  Resolve the latest release version through DistributionClient without downloading assets.
  Print the local SpecDD version when it exists.
  Print that no local SpecDD version was found when .specdd/bootstrap.md does not exist.
  Print the latest remote SpecDD version.
  Validate local and latest release version values through SpecDDVersion.
  Compare local Version with the latest release version through SpecDDVersion when a local Version exists.
  Inform the user when the local Version is older than the latest release version.
  Include https://specdd.ai/changelog/ when informing the user that an update is available.
  Return whether an update is available.
  Return the local version when found.
  Return the latest remote version.

Must not:
  Download, verify, or apply distribution assets.
  Modify files.
  Treat a missing local bootstrap as an available update.

Depends on:
  CliError
  Logger
  SpecDDVersion
  BootstrapMetadata
  DistributionClient

Exposes:
  UpdateChecker.check(request)

Accepts:
  UpdateCheckRequest

Returns:
  UpdateCheckResult

Raises:
  UpdateCheckError
  UpdateCheckInvalidVersionError

Handles:
  missing local bootstrap
  local Version equal to latest release version
  local Version newer than latest release version
  local Version older than latest release version
  invalid local Version
  invalid latest release version
